text: Muara Teweh (abbreviated: MTWhttp://ftp.paudni.kemdiknas.go.id/paudni/2011/06/SNI_7657-2010_Singkatan_Nama_Kota.pdf) is a city located in the province of Central Kalimantan. It is the capital of North Barito Regency. ==Climate== Muara Teweh has a tropical rainforest climate (Af) with heavy rainfall year-round. ==References== Category:Populated places in Central Kalimantan Category:Regency seats of Central Kalimantan
title: Muara Teweh
